OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary has
OL,8,Fsaid he appreciates why families of
OL,9,Fsome Troubles victims remain sceptical
OL,10,Fabout a new investigatory and truth
OL,11,Frecovery body.
OL,13,FHilary Benn said he knows reform of
OL,14,Flegislation underpinning the
OL,15,FIndependent Commission for
OL,16,FReconciliation and Information
OL,17,FRecovery (ICRIR) is required to secure
OL,18,Fthe confidence of bereaved relatives.
