OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,FThe ICRIR was set up by the last
OL,8,Fgovernment as part of its contentious
OL,9,FLegacy Act.
OL,11,FWhile the Labour government has vowed
OL,12,Fto repeal parts of the Act, including
OL,13,Fthe contentious offer of conditional
OL,14,Fimmunity for perpetrators of Troubles
OL,15,Fkillings, it has decided to retain the
OL,16,Fcommission.
