OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,FSome families who lost loved ones
OL,8,Fduring the conflict have vowed not to
OL,9,Fengage with the commission, claiming
OL,10,Fit lacks the teeth and independence to
OL,11,Fproperly re-examine their cases.
OL,13,FMr Benn, writing in Saturday's Irish
OL,14,FNews, insisted he was committed to
OL,15,Fmaking changes.
OL,17,F"Everybody I have spoken to agrees
OL,18,Fthat there needs to be a means of
OL,19,Fconducting investigations and of
OL,20,Frecovering information," he wrote.
