OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,F"And we do now have, for the first
OL,8,Ftime, an independent judge-led
OL,9,Fcommission, responsible for doing both
OL,10,Fthese things.
OL,12,F"I am the first to acknowledge that
OL,13,Fthe legislation that established the
OL,14,Fcommission needs to be changed and I
OL,15,Fappreciate why, after all these years,
OL,16,Fand given the origins of the Legacy
OL,17,FAct, there is scepticism about it.
OL,19,F"I know that reforms will be needed to
OL,20,Fsecure the confidence of families.
