OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,F"But a growing number of requests for
OL,8,Finvestigations and information are now
OL,9,Fbeing made to the commission, over 120
OL,10,Fat the last count, and the Northern
OL,11,FIreland Courts have been clear that it
OL,12,Fhas the powers it needs to carry out
OL,13,Findependent, human rights-compliant
OL,14,Finvestigations.
