OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,F"What's more, the legislation I will
OL,8,Fpropose will ensure that the
OL,9,Fcommission is, in specific
OL,10,Fcircumstances, able to hold public
OL,11,Fhearings, take sworn evidence from
OL,12,Findividuals, and ensure families have
OL,13,Feffective representation."
OL,15,FMr Benn said one of the advantages of
OL,16,Fthe commission was that it can quickly
OL,17,Fget to work, as he noted that its team
OL,18,Fof investigators was growing.
