OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,F"The commission also has full police
OL,8,Fpowers to help find answers without
OL,9,Fthe long years of waiting that are
OL,10,Foften involved with public inquiries,
OL,11,Fwhich must establish staff, premises
OL,12,Fand processes from scratch," he added.
OL,14,F"There are a number of families,
OL,15,Fincluding the family of (murdered GAA
OL,16,Fofficial) Sean Brown, whose inquests
OL,17,Fwere brought to a premature end (by
OL,18,Fthe Legacy Act), and who continue to
OL,19,Fexperience great pain and suffering.
