OL,3,CReforms of new Troubles commission
OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,F"For each of these families, I want to
OL,8,Fensure that there is a full, thorough
OL,9,Fand independent investigation into the
OL,10,Fdeath of their loved one as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,F"I urge all those still searching for
OL,14,Fanswers, for justice or for
OL,15,Facknowledgement of what happened, to
OL,16,Ftalk to the commission to hear and
OL,17,Fdiscuss what they propose, knowing
OL,18,Fthat the government will strengthen it
OL,19,Fin our forthcoming legislation."
