OL,4,Cneeded to secure trust of families,
OL,5,Csays Benn
OL,7,FThe Labour MP said the "complexity and
OL,8,Fsensitivity" of dealing with the
OL,9,Flegacy of the past required a need to
OL,10,F"build as broad a consensus as
OL,11,Fpossible".
OL,13,F"I am determined, with the help of all
OL,14,Finterested parties, including the
OL,15,FIrish government, to achieve this," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"Nothing will ever ease the pain that
OL,19,Fso many families endure to this day.
