OL,7,FMr Brown, 61, the chairman of Bellaghy
OL,8,FWolfe Tones GAA club in Co
OL,9,FLondonderry, was ambushed, kidnapped
OL,10,Fand murdered by loyalist
OL,11,Fparamilitaries as he locked the gates
OL,12,Fof the club in May 1997.
OL,14,FNo-one has ever been convicted of his
OL,15,Fkilling.
OL,17,FIn December, High Court judge Mr
OL,18,FJustice Humphreys issued an order
OL,19,Fcompelling the Government to set up a
OL,20,Fpublic inquiry.
